Key to the species groups of 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Medvedev &amp; Dang" authorityYear="1981" box="[682,842,999,1022]" class="Insecta" family="Chrysomelidae" genus="Hesperopenna" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="7" pageNumber="722" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
